","msg":"屌，我住咗樂富10年，由仆街領匯第一日開始裝修我已經屌9佢地，屌撚到今日<br />\n裝修之後呢區無好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2684c7d99913e0e37d681273b824cb5ac89c318d","tid":104070,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T21:03:39.000Z","msg":"幾時執架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼10年冇去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係記得有一層有歡樂天地同有間泰國野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有間好大嘅吉之島"},{"pid":"b81b659fcd1538bb68b6c3913b03b36363b745f8","tid":104070,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T21:12:01.000Z","msg":"我記得五十嵐位置係M記果條斜路<br />\neurogogo果個位，以前樓上有間茶樓<br />\n現時百佳啲位置，以前應該係jusco<br />\n我記得可以係巴士站直接穿jusco入商場<br />\n不過而家好多都變晒lu~<br />\n<br />\n利申 讀樂富隔離間u，但以前已經成日去樂富"},{"pid":"0453e6d13934e007d6736eb396a52fd898cf9a7b","tid":104070,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T23:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想記返樂富中心既格局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔太記得啦 但以前真係覺得樂富個吉之島好好行<br />\n<br />\n層層都分得勁好 超市 男裝女裝 童裝玩具 電器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最記得係超市果層 中間扶手電梯有間龍鬚糖<br />\n成日扭計叫老豆買<br />\n<br />\n同埋玩具部隔離有間餐廳 細個成日食佢d兒童餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是咪現在的Uny?"},{"pid":"1a4fa1b446d32d85476508e4f309cb9f2ca40c99","tid":104070,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T20:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebd2b2792cfbdc68d616db3bab9c9a4f5b4fb4d","tid":104070,"uid":3692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:53:23.000Z","msg":"街坊<img src=\"/